recordings.rmk: Background loudspeaker from park tour guides.  2 birds seen about 15' off the ground in mid-story.
Photographed

Many other birds in the background, but the soft "eeu?" call was of a recently fledged Black-headed Trogon sitting in an 8 m tall tree (about 6 m from the ground) in Pacific dry forest. The two parents were also seen nearby.
